Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月月殖民地的存在\N本来就很令人惊讶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且光之族好像问题更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.96,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被绑走了\N被迫与美丽小姐和姬娜在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后戈图还派出MS大队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后莫名奇妙的光之族与教祖都奉承我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且拉莎拉与莎拉莎,是同一个人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.52,0:01:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十五话\N幻影殖民地 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.15,0:02:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么?拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉?我不是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.94,0:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莎拉莎.月\N统治光之族的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着,罗尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要与这个少年谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事态糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.77,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是教祖啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.09,0:02:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,你必须以救世主的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.36,0:02:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我把光之教传播到全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.07,0:02:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是再说笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之族的教祖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.23,0:02:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想利用你们的力量\N把光之族的宗教传播到全宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.20,0:02:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个作法一定会破坏\N月月殖民地的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年!把你的生命交给月月吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为我离开这里的向导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你振作点,拉莎拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被施予催眠术了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快清醒啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无礼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉!快清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种无理的人\N不可能是救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这些人关进地下牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.61,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人疯了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.89,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.95,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.17,0:03:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们省省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的人走开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.47,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事...全身有点痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追,别让那些小孩跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先回去亚加玛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZZ高达在神殿的前面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那时候不上去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管矛有多危险\N被射中还是会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉那女孩想干什么阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.99,0:04:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度你\N看到美丽的女人就头昏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.13,0:04:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看到我怎么没头昏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟比查打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟比查又没有订婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查说过类似的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊?可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉的人来了,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉?他们用小钢珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请从后面上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后我在解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度加快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,莫迪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪?\N干什么用这种眼光看着我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去安多拉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个说来话长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我帮忙救了你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,这女孩不是莎拉莎吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.24,0:05:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?他是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莎拉莎.月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉,这倒底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你们\N见过姐姐拉莎拉才追过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐莎拉莎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.19,0:05:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你们是双胞胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐被奉为光之族的教祖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就变的自大起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.18,0:05:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她以为\N只要把光之教传播到全宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争就会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是光靠各位的两艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.34,0:05:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将光之教传播出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为打仗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会相信这教义吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是配合祥和的月光波长\N和平活下去的教义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看这个还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,限于月月地方就好了\N为什么他想离开殖民地呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.26,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是她向往\N殖民地之前的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.69,0:06:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是过度相信力量的错误欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奴娜地下道的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灯点亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗? 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手电筒不是比较方便吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.61,0:06:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?万一灯熄了\N就表示附近有毒瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边走,请到神殿下面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要坐这个去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不会动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许可以动..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.79,0:07:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了!要打开电源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.36,0:07:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你们有人精通机器\N实在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很荣幸帮你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却背叛雅加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了赚钱还想把高达压成废铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被人讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来就是卖废铁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是会使用机器的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在思考\N搜索秘密地下道的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.02,0:07:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点,相信机器力量的人\N除了破坏之外不会带来什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.77,0:07:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个凯特尔正说明了\N机器是多么无力的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.19,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些愚蠢的人\N连这个都不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,他们很温驯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛之船也交给他们控制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.99,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法,只好藉助他们的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种待遇太不人道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别轻举妄动,受伤就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.75,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那教祖说画像废铁班\N完全不可理喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老啰唆,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方不大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑与矛都很难用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别一直拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是ㄚ,你欠我一个人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,我自己解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有办法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持原状比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.33,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位,快到这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教祖怎么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,详情以后再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了扩张光之教\N你们把船借给我用就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是跟亚加玛联手了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎.月大人\N成为宇宙的主人之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传送一个殖民地给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多么荣幸的条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.29,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是花费弹药\N而夺的一个殖民星的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越深入了解这个殖民地\N我的心越被光之教吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到我这样的小人\N也能成为光之子民啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.53,0:09:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯帮忙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了表示我的决心\N我很乐意效劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.58,0:09:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,把那具大机器拆掉\N丢到安多拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.34,0:09:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终点是亚加玛所在的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抢回ZZ高达再回亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又要绑我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是亚加玛的俘虏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道安多拉的动向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜也过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到亚加玛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.47,0:10:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉,对不起\N带我去ZZ高达那里好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.17,0:10:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,我们也要去凯特尔那儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让凯特行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.03,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯特尔...\N用神殿旁边的巨大怪东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.07,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔特 在月月人丢弃机器后\N就不在移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.43,0:10:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直被丢再那里\N成为代表软弱无力的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.27,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是它可以开动\N人们该会注意到过去的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还未找到安多拉根亚加玛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.28,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,雷达发现类似第一世代\N殖民地的物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 殖民地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到其他类似的人工物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西好像放很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不动的话还是卖给博物馆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看ZZ高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的享分解它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有办法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是受教祖之托的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉,我要上去驾驶舱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们引开看守的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我潜入ZZ高达里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以输给比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以动,电池也在可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.59,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁妨碍我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可疑的人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里!追阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,你在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...比查,快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,ZZ高达...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到年代这么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一定要开动才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓到他\N这边!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.69,0:13:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛\N不许动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手,捷度,你想要杀人吗?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开,比查,不然我真的会刺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪,不能再快点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.48,0:13:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.76,0:13:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,拉莎拉,拉下开关吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不动啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别爬上来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以让他们坐上巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!别在爬上来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会塌下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入了,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到我了!\N你们小心被踩扁阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷..捷度,住手,很危险阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快连络安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派出加煞C队抵抗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨神动了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨神动了,神愤怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲阿,干掉它们吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肃静!大家冷静!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨神飞上天空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.29,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想用安多拉的巨神\N打败飞上天的巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.08,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来...那个少年并不是救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜,哥哥现在就去救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开!敢妨碍我就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉舱口,ZZ高达来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别阻挠!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸了,MS甲板受到攻击\N加煞C爆炸了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜...不要紧吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的ZZ高达!\N竟然攻击安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.37,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明大人\N发现安多拉在月月殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正受到攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N刚接到无线电话内容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派出龙飞,我要出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是巨神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨神愤怒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.22,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎大人,在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图大人,巨神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止巨神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然月月之地会被摧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打败ZZ高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地是不会有和平的\N我们是为此而战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是巨神是不可以开动的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.89,0:16:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,这次行了,保证能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.38,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不动?动阿\N快点动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.45,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,动了,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到姐姐身边去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N不愧是新式MS,很敏捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是安多拉受到攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.72,0:17:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以引来露卡的莉娜\N不会有事吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥,人质莉娜被关在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!在资料室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,资料室吗?好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开,我没空理你们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续压住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用雷射枪打死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯特尔!\N动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是..是什么一回事?神像动了!\N不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们阿,不必害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔特是机器,本来就会动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神像觉醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了纠正月月人的错误\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不该害怕机器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.39,0:18:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可听被我驱逐的妹妹说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教祖大人,请平息巨神之怒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗尔!\N戈图他们在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们该负起责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧,凯尔特会解决问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走啊,我们的神像动了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.99,0:18:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在回去亚加玛\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪,剩下的拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜!莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你!把莉娜还给我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!你想杀死莉娜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要救回莉娜的话,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拿露卡来换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.61,0:19:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿露卡来换?他再说什么阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.35,0:20:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,神像赢了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔特!凯尔特打败外面的敌人了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.25,0:20:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外界有很多类似的机器?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐因为凯尔特没开动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而认定光之教是对的\N这就太武断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我想利用机器之船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对外界宣扬光之教是错的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪那浑蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然帮助捷度他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的! 我另有原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到安卡拉再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.59,0:20:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图先生\N你们躲再哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的时刻却躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.94,0:20:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗尔,为了将宇宙传到外界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把莎拉莎推上教祖之位的人是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小殖民地太难生存了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样有错吗?我没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让不知情的月月人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.61,0:21:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为宇宙战争的牺牲者\N难道就是对的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是自愿驾驶MS的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为坐上战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.84,0:21:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹还被敌人抓走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.58,0:21:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听着月月是连地球联邦军\N和亚古捷斯都忘记的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个情况才是最好的啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.50,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...被遗忘的感觉太寂寞了\N活的越老越是感伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉度,我们走吧\N不是会有新战舰会再过来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你妹妹平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,莎拉莎\N外界是很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,虽说是井底之蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.23,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但殖民地内的生态循环还算正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.51,0:22:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总比大而不当的殖民地好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.52,0:22:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救回莉娜之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再到那里玩吧

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.27,0:23:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把补给物资搬到亚加玛的奇怪的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.07,0:23:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不小心把戈图的MS队带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈图为了完好地得到亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.98,0:24:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们停靠在拉比安玫瑰的时候进行MS战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.15,0:24:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶~ 没完没了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛的肉搏战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候才能见到莉娜？
